title: Quantization tool is gone?
body_html:
if you run bazel build tensorflow/contrib/quantization/tools:quantize_graph with the latest code, it report error: can't not find the files.

if you go to https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/tree/master/tensorflow/contrib/quantization folder, the files are not here already and there is no tools folder.

body:
if you run **bazel build tensorflow/contrib/quantization/tools:quantize_graph** with the latest code, it report error: can't not find the files.

if you go to **https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/tree/master/tensorflow/contrib/quantization** folder, the files are not here already and there is no **tools** folder.
